<taxonomicName id="2D0134B9A7B85B78FB3586B12D49A960" family="Fabaceae" lsidName="" pageId="4" pageNumber="83" rank="family">Fabaceae</taxonomicName>
). Specimens from these populations will feed on 
<taxonomicName id="BEADFE739430602E5B482C7C8DB6D1CC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Polygonum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Polygonum chinense" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="83" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="chinense">Polygonum chinense</taxonomicName>
if switched from their original host plant.
</paragraph>
